		text: `As a UX designer, I dreamt of working in a place that offers growth, product awareness, and the feeling that my actions tangibly change someone's experiences. Bethink provides all of this and more. As an added bonus, it comes with fantastic people, a culture of openness and feedback, and a friendly atmosphere.`,
